data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
This unstable method does not trim textures to the engine's expected length, and instead tries to import at the original file's length. May reduce glitches with imported textures, however may lead to wider offset issues.
Enabling/disabling this will require a manual reset of your game's files.

data.name: enableExperimentalTextureImport.ToolTip
data.value: Enable to-size texture imports. This unstable method does not trim textures to the engine's expected length, and instead tries to import at the original file's length. May reduce glitches with imported textures, however may lead to wider offset issues.
